data.title: Lasse Mårtenson
data.meta_description: Lasse Mårtenson. Composer: Harjunpää ja kiusantekijät. Lasse Mårtenson was born on 24 September 1934 in Helsinki, Finland. He was a composer and actor, known for Harjunpää ja kiusantekijät (1993), Heisse Katze? (1968) and Rampe & Naukkis - Kaikkien aikojen superpari (1990). He was married to Sari Angervo, Anna-Liisa Ehrnrooth, Siw Malmkvist and Carita Wilhelmsson. He died on 14 May 2016 in Espoo, Finland.
data.text: Lasse Mårtenson was born on September 24, 1934 in Helsinki, Finland. He was a composer and actor, known for Harjunpää ja kiusantekijät (1993), Heisse Katze? (1968) and Rampe & Naukkis - Kaikkien aikojen superpari (1990). He was married to Sari Angervo, Anna-Liisa Ehrnrooth, Siw Malmkvist and Carita Wilhelmsson. He died on May 14, 2016 in Espoo, Finland.
